&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Availability to work full USA hour shifts in EST, CST, or PST time zone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Work experience: A minimum of 4-5 years of experience as an accountant&lt;/li&gt;
